386→                        <div id="content">Let $d\geq 2$ and $n\geq 2$. Let $f_d(n)$ be maximal such that there exists some set of $n$ points $A\subseteq \mathbb{R}^d$, with diameter $1$, in which the distance 1 occurs between $f_d(n)$ many pairs of points in $A$. Estimate $f_d(n)$.</div>
